{"Sid":0,"Did":126885,"Id":"604510","Title":"羅東震安宮石柱警語銘刻","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/92c3d127-d558-4fdf-a112-fda31cdd63f7/109-her-pa-2477-202011141429575faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collection/b9850878-3410-414f-8287-055fb1b20bdf/109-her-pa-2477-202011141429575faf66a9552b81.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n　　在臺灣傳統移民社會中，經常可見遊民，俗稱「羅漢腳」。在《噶瑪蘭廳志》中即提到：「臺灣一種無田宅無妻子、不士不農、不工不賈、不負戴道路，俗指謂羅漢腳；嫖賭摸竊，械鬪樹旗，靡所不為。曷言乎羅漢腳也？謂其單身遊食四方，隨處結黨；且衫褲不全，赤腳終生也。」羅漢腳因無宅為家，因此經常為求遮風避雨，而寄宿廟宇之中。\n\n　　羅東震安宮在1923（大正12）年開始重修，或因廟貌即將一新，未免新落成之廟宇有成為羅漢腳在廟內寄宿，有違神聖廟殿尊嚴，因此特別在前殿石柱以及正殿後殿間廂廊廊柱上銘刻以「注意　污腳勿踏椅頂　廟內切勿安眠」的警語。同樣的警語，也被銘刻在1923（大正12）年重修落成的羅東奠安宮的石柱上。此警語的銘刻，也說明了當時的廟宇仍常有羅漢腳窩居休息的社會現象。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.770462","Keyword_Latitude":"24.673551","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/9D14E4A0-8161-4131-8C1E-25102A9EA100","Original_Identifier":"604510","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"石雕 / 羅東奠安宮 / 羅漢腳","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2021/01/06 18:35:30","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣羅東鎮中正路35號","longitude":"121.770462","latitude":"24.673551","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"無","writer":"蔡明志/ 林鴻文","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/bd51592a-0f34-40da-b82c-a0e3277b3cd1/109-her-pa-2477-re-202011141432535faf66a9552b80.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-11-15/ba63115f-ebd8-4618-a123-eaa303a942dd/collectionOpen/e1c2741e-3968-4053-9291-cacbf9b3e202/109-her-pa-24